This is a Python package to handle ZIO devices. It include varius python's
modules which describe all the ZIO's objects:

- zObject: is an abstract class for most of the ZIO object (zDev, zCset,
           zChannel, zBuf, zTrig)
- zDev: it describes the zio_device structure of a ZIO device
- zCset: it describes the zio_cset structure of a ZIO device
- zChan: it describes the zio_channel structure of a ZIO device
- zBuf: it describes the zio_bi struture of a ZIO buffer
- zTrig: it describes the zio_ti structure of a ZIO trigger
